{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"mg7066wnd3agqrjxcxmrxkx","title":"Word","desc":"","updated":1662568319952,"created":1661540059329,"custom":{},"fname":"publish.word","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Zendron"},"contentHash":"6cccefb1f2584cdf46f18a1e04b01e6f","links":[],"anchors":{"merge-tools":{"type":"header","text":"Merge Tools","value":"merge-tools","line":7,"column":0,"depth":2},"linux":{"type":"header","text":"Linux","value":"linux","line":10,"column":0,"depth":3},"macos":{"type":"header","text":"MacOS","value":"macos","line":16,"column":0,"depth":3},"windows":{"type":"header","text":"Windows","value":"windows","line":22,"column":0,"depth":3},"issues":{"type":"header","text":"Issues","value":"issues","line":26,"column":0,"depth":3}},"children":[],"parent":"k0qo53e6jvew0mcyv49bu0e","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"word\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#word\"></a>Word</h1>\n<h2 id=\"merge-tools\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#merge-tools\"></a>Merge Tools</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Docx merge tools are limited as it looks difficult to merge the xml.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"linux\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#linux\"></a>Linux</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Ventto/odocxmerge\">Linux option</a>\n<ul>\n<li>This is specific to linux</li>\n<li>Only works on linux. Requires <code>resgen</code>.\n<ul>\n<li>Attempted download on MacOS: <code>resgen: command not found</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"macos\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#macos\"></a>MacOS</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>It seems this must be done manually...</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3FYzP_kWq24\">youtube tutorial</a>\n<ul>\n<li>This works well enough</li>\n<li>My use case is only for cover page and the rest of the body</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"windows\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#windows\"></a>Windows</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/jamessantiago/DocxMerge\">Windows Option</a></li>\n<li>Looks simple enough but there are known issues like the ordering of the documents. But it should be navigable. See <a href=\"https://github.com/jamessantiago/DocxMerge/issues/2\">issue</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"issues\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#issues\"></a>Issues</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>TOC out of order <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/25591517/pandoc-inserting-pages-before-generated-table-of-contents\">stackoverflow</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"nuyfwd7iokzd7m9oax0cdx5","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1662428184246,"created":1661538521294,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Zendron"},"contentHash":"9185b031f95deeced1275adbefc49c09","links":[],"anchors":{"parameter_estimation":{"type":"header","text":"Parameter_Estimation","value":"parameter_estimation","line":7,"column":0,"depth":2},"paper-export":{"type":"header","text":"Paper Export","value":"paper-export","line":9,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["m7o7r4jqe4jdwgsh3ia8sa4","2fib55e8qqux9scimc7a9gn","tz8wfy0bidyoi7cew6pxfi4","k0qo53e6jvew0mcyv49bu0e","xxezmgby3v2mlneka3t295g","9gt33emg7725ksj2t7f4p4v"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"## Parameter_Estimation\n\n## Paper Export\n- [paper.docx](./notes/export/paper.docx)\n- [paper.pdf](./notes/export/paper.pdf)"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableExportPodV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"alwaysPrompt"}},"insertNote":{"initialValue":"templates"},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"r